Cybersecurity

Siemens takes a holistic approach to addressing cybersecurity in the best interest of our customers. It is essential to the comprehensive protection of both industry and society from internal and external cyberattacks.

Our cybersecurity governance and policies The Cybersecurity Board (CSB), chaired by the Global Chief Cybersecurity Officer, is responsible for the implementation and coordination of cybersecurity throughout Siemens. The member of the Siemens AG Managing Board responsible for cybersecurity is part of the CSB, as are the Chief Cybersecurity Officers of each of Siemensâ€™ businesses.